@gateway = https://localhost:5001

### Gateway dashboard
GET {{gateway}}/api/dashboard

### Event catalog through Gateway
GET {{gateway}}/api/events

### Sessions for Cloud Native Summit through Gateway
GET {{gateway}}/api/events/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111/sessions

### Register an attendee through Gateway
POST {{gateway}}/api/registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "sessionId": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaa1",
  "attendeeName": "Alex Morgan",
  "attendeeEmail": "alex.morgan@example.com"
}

### Recent notification records through Gateway
GET {{gateway}}/api/notifications/recent

### Node.js recommendations through Gateway
GET {{gateway}}/api/recommendations?eventId=11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
